{"tid":2381364,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★住在碧街圍封附近的夏小姐說，不擔心自己的寓所會被圍封","createTime":"2021-01-26T13:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T05:53:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b120daaeebd23c0d4b9fc30b502ee8e57803683b","tid":2381364,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1572489_2_L_20210126202255.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1572489_2_L_20210126202255.jpg&h=f60b8062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n夏小姐說，不擔心自己的寓所會被圍封<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，大批警員到場以鐵閘封鎖街道出入口，有警員把守，亦有吊臂車駛進。<br />\n<br />\n有不少市民在場圍觀。有住在受限區域附近的居民林先生說，雖然自己不是住在受限區域，但都感到擔心，原本落街跑步，但跑完步後就發現住所附近被封，他說會自己做好防疫，清潔雙手及戴口罩。另一名<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>住在附近的居民夏小姐說，不擔心自己的寓所會被圍封</strong></span>，但已買定食物及物資，以防一旦被圍封，可以在家煮食。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572489-20210126.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572489-20210126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=0ed0ed12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1572489-20210126.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0ffa6f53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1572489-20210126.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7e4d3ff9d97c1e9392de79b6b013072d0f2c7177","tid":2381364,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T13:38:06.000Z","msg":"on9藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},